Earth 2 (000 - 025 + extras) (2012 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire)


Featuring an alternate earth within the DC Multiverse, Earth 2 is a "Second Wave" title of DC's The New 52 initiative, featuring a reworked Justice Society Of America, amongst other characters. It features Alan Scott, Jay Garrick, Hawkgirl,and Khalid Ben-Hassin in its main cast.
